extends layout

block content
  main.about-page
    .container
      a.back-link(href="/")
        svg(width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2")
          path(d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7")
        | Back to Home

      .about-content
        h1.page-title How It Works

        section.about-section
          h2.section-title The Concept
          p.section-text
            | Mood DJ for Footballers is an emotional sideline experience that combines music, visuals, and
            | AI-generated content to create personalized emotional journeys based on football scenarios. Whether
            | you've just scored the winning goal or been benched for the final, we'll create a unique experience that
            | matches your emotional state.

        section.about-section
          h2.section-title Technology Behind It
          .tech-grid
            .tech-card
              h3.tech-title 🎵 Music Integration
              p.tech-description
                | We use music APIs like Spotify to select tracks that perfectly match the emotional tone of your
                | selected scenario.
            .tech-card
              h3.tech-title 🖼️ Visual Experience
              p.tech-description
                | Dynamic backgrounds and GIFs are sourced from GIPHY and other visual libraries to create an
                | immersive atmosphere.
            .tech-card
              h3.tech-title 🎙️ AI Commentary
              p.tech-description
                | We use OpenAI's API to generate unique motivational quotes and commentary for each scenario.
            .tech-card
              h3.tech-title 😎 Mood Matching
              p.tech-description
                | Our algorithm analyzes the emotional context of your scenario to create a fitting footballer
                | persona.

        section.about-section
          h2.section-title Future Features
          ul.features-list
            li.feature-item
              span.feature-emoji 🎤
              span Voice synthesis to generate a coach's voice with ElevenLabs
            li.feature-item
              span.feature-emoji 🎬
              span Timeline of scenes for a cinematic experience
            li.feature-item
              span.feature-emoji 🔄
              span Custom scenario creation
            li.feature-item
              span.feature-emoji 💾
              span Save and share your favorite experiences

        .cta-section
          a.cta-button(href="/scenarios") Try It Now
